<div class="wrap">	<h2>Content by Country - Info Page</h2><div id="logo"><img title="www.soluciones-internet.es" src="http://www.soluciones-internet.es/wp-content/themes/soluciones-internet/images/soluciones-internet-logo.png" alt="Soluciones Internet" /></div><!-- /#logo --><div id="texto">  <p>Wellcome to Content by Country information page.</p>  <p>Have you ever need to show a content only for visitors of the country you want?<br />    This plugin will do this for you. <br />    Simply choose the country you want to show the content for and done.<br />    This plugin use the ipinfodb.com API.</p><p>This plugin was originally made to hide publicity for non Spanish people.</p><ol>  <li> Go to http://ipinfodb.com/register.php and register por an API Key. (It's free)</li>    <li> Enter the plugin's config page in the CbC tab</li>    <li> Enter the Key in the API Key folder. If the field is empty the plugin use the default Key.</li>    <li> Select the Country for which you want to limit the content from the drop down menu.</li>    <li> Clic the Update Config button</li>    <li> Create or edit a post and enter the shortcode with your private content.</li>    e.g.:  [privatecontent] ONLY SHOW FOR DESIRED COUNTRY [/privatecontent]</li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Remember you need to sign for an API key in <a href="http://ipinfodb.com/register.php" target="_blank">IpinfoDB</a> and enter in the proper config field.</p><p>If you don't have an API key don't worry. Simply leave the field empty.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you consider usefull this plugin, please donate.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post"><input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick"><input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="RZEF7ZXX5J7EN"><input type="image" src="https://www.paypal.com/es_ES/ES/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal. La forma rÃ¡pida y segura de pagar en Internet."><img alt="" border="0" s